    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and totally ready to hit the road with its next owner. It runs like a dream and has been treated with a lot of care, so you\u2019re getting a really solid car that\u2019s ready for all your upcoming adventures. I\u2019d love for you to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love how it feels!",
