    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E92 M3 powered by the iconic S65 B40 naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant features an 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies, delivering exceptional throttle response. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including a documented rod bearing service using VAC treated bearings and replacement of the throttle actuators. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides a tactile connection to the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal traction under load. The suspension retains its Electronic Damper Control (EDC) functionality, offering adjustable damping rates for varied road conditions. While the Interlagos Blue finish shows minor road rash consistent with enthusiast use, the structural integrity of the subframe and the health of the VANOS system are excellent. This is a performance-oriented example ready for spirited driving.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance.",
