    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained, clean, and runs like a dream! It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something reliable that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32000.0,
