    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical enthusiast maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system refresh with an upgraded aluminum radiator to prevent heat soak. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed control arm bushings, providing the tactile hydraulic steering feedback these chassis are known for. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the drivetrain remains potent with linear power delivery to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
